history.content:
189 brings back painful flashbacks for me in general, but the schedule is doable I guess, depending what you've taken and how you did in them.

If 170 and 126/127 went well for you, 189 could be done with two other tech courses, but will be a decent amount of work.

Most people in my experience have difficulty with 61c. You might be able to pull it off with 189. You know yourself better than I do Mr./Ms. Anon, but it will take a lot of work no matter.

186 feels like an extension of 61b but somehow less painful. Maybe the intro courses are just more traumatic.

If you have flexibility, might be better to split up 61c and 189, but it can be done

As title. Has anyone taken this schedule before?

Thank you all so much!
history.subject: Sp20: Is 61C + 189 + 186 doable?
